title: feat: Ability to parse multiple feeds URLs.
message:
feat: Ability to parse multiple feeds URLs.

Changes done:
 1. Parse multiple feed URLs.
 2. Ability to cancel the request whenever required.
 3. Updated the demo project for better understanding.
 4. Updated default image and updated the library version in readme.

title: feat: Major changes, replaced jsoup with SimpleXml parser.
message:
feat: Major changes, replaced jsoup with SimpleXml parser.

Changes done:
 1. Library now uses SimpleXml parser for parsing rss feeds.
 2. XML feeds are fetched asynchronously using okhttp as a networking client.
 3. Removed AsyncTask API from the library.
 4. Removed AppCompat v7 library as it no longer required.
 5. Removed jsoup library as it is no longer required.
 6. Updated compileSdkVersion, targetSdkVersion and buildToolsVersion of the library.
 7. Updated sample code for testing library's functionality.
